original: Frieberg, Johan Axel, major, Uddevalla, f. 28/5/96 i Hedemora av öv:-löjtn. Ludvig F. o. Elüen Bolin. G. 21 m. Kersti Larsson-Hytte. Barn: Ulla-Brita f. 22, Anders 24, Marit 25, Ulf 32, Karin 39. — Stud:ex. 14, off :ex. 16. Fänr. v. Dalreg. 16, löjtn. 19, kapten 36 major i reg. 40, major v. Bohusl. reg. 40.
translated: Frieberg, Johan Axel, Major, from Uddevalla. Born on 28/5/1896 in Hedemora to Lieutenant Ludvig F. and Elüen Bolin. Married Kersti Larsson-Hytte in 1921. Children: Ulla-Brita (born 1922), Anders (born 1924), Marit (born 1925), Ulf (born 1932), Karin (born 1939). Completed secondary school in 1914 and military officer training in 1916. Promoted to lieutenant in 1919 and to captain in 1936. Became a major in the regiment of 1940 and served as a major in the Bohuslän regiment in the same year.
